- Grckoljubac.

87
00:11:40,868 --> 00:11:43,787
- Koliko dobro govoris engleski!
- Osam godina u Bruklinu.

88
00:11:43,954 --> 00:11:46,540
- Bruklin? Zezas me.
- Obalska straza.

89
00:11:46,707 --> 00:11:49,042
A sada radim ovde na obali Pireusa.

90
00:11:49,209 --> 00:11:50,919
- Pivo.
- Dva piva.

91
00:11:51,086 --> 00:11:53,755
