94
00:12:01,388 --> 00:12:04,725
- Samo pravim neke zabeleske.
- Sta si ti?

95
00:12:05,559 --> 00:12:07,936
Ja sam filozof amater.

96
00:12:09,730 --> 00:12:11,398
Ostajes dugo u Grckoj?

97
00:12:11,565 --> 00:12:14,610
Mozda. Ja tragam za necim u Grckoj.

98
00:12:15,277 --> 00:12:16,320
Za cim?

99
00:12:17,154 --> 00:12:19,948
-Obecaj da se neces smejati?
